com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationservice.impl.responses

Class BackupResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationservice.impl.responses.Response
      • com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationservice.impl.responses.BackupResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSerializable, IdentifiedDataSerializable

    public final class BackupResponse
extends Response
    The {Response} for a BackupOperation. So when a operation like Map.put is done, backup operations are send to the backup partitions. For the initial Map.put to complete, the NormalResponse needs to return, but also the BackupResponse to make sure that the change is written to the expected number of backups.
